vernac_cmds: Lemma not_digit_when (c : ascii) (x : nat) : (nat_of_ascii c < 48) \/ (57 < nat_of_ascii c) -> unit_digit x <> c.
Lemma unit_digit_ascii : forall n, digit_of_ascii (unit_digit n) = Some (n mod 10).
Lemma decimal_thousand : forall n, n < 256 -> (n / 100) mod 10 * 100 + (n / 10) mod 10 * 10 + n mod 10 = n.
Lemma ascii_256 : forall c, nat_of_ascii c < 256.
Lemma unthree_three_digit (c : ascii) : let n := nat_of_ascii c in unthree_digit (unit_digit (n / 100)) (unit_digit (n / 10)) (unit_digit n) = Some (ascii_of_nat n).
Lemma read_show_quoted_string : forall (s : string), read_quoted_string (show_quoted_string s) = Some s.
Lemma read_show_string : forall (s : string), read_string (show s) = Some s.
